description: Welcome home to 121 F St. This unique open floor plan home offers versatility at its finest. Step into the expansive living area that effortlessly transitions into the dining room, creating a harmonious flow throughout the space. Your exclusive outdoor area of the dining room offers the perfect blend of indoor-outdoor living. Modern spacious kitchen fully equipped with gas cooking to whip up delicious meals. Spacious king sized primary bedroom with ample closet space. The second bedroom can serve as a spacious home office or guest bedroom. Private laundry in basement, extra storage and low condo fees. Situated in the heart of South Boston, this condo provides convenient access to all your favorite Southie hotspots, beautiful beaches, and Broadway station.
